title: THE BURNS and ALLEN SHOW -- George Becomes an Author
description:
This episode (also known as "Gracie Renews Her Driver's License"
is one of the more realistic ones, because George Burns
actually was writing his biography starting in 1954.  It was released
the following year as his first of at least a half-dozen books.

His "My Life with Gracie" in 1988 (which he also released as an
audiobook on cassette and CD) was a best-seller.
